{"tid":574192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河北男心臟病發吐血無人理　撒百元鈔票求救","createTime":"2018-02-27T07:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T09:07:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d58a892c8c32ef856d1946b544fa30d9f33ecfa8","tid":574192,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180227/photo/bkncn-20180227103900246-0227_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180227120104\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180227%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180227103900246-0227_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180227120104&h=62f90fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地不時傳出利用民眾同情心呃錢的騙案，令不少市民即使看到突發事故，都寧願冷漠應對。一名李姓男子上周六（24日）在河北石家莊火車站突然心臟病發，吐血並癱坐地上，多名途人見狀都未有伸出援手，為了吸引途人注意，李男只好扔出多張百元鈔票，希望獲路人幫忙。 <br />\n<br />\n據警員憶述，當日他正在東廣場巡邏，遠遠看到一名男子突然彎腰並半跪在地，又在背囊翻找東西，其後更癱倒地上。警員起初以為他只是喝醉酒，走近一看驚見他面前有兩攤鮮血，地上還有數張百元鈔票，且右手抓着一瓶速效救心丸。 <br />\n<br />\n警員立即上前協助，之後按李男所說，餵他吃下幾粒救心丸，同時請醫護人員趕來查看其情況。幸而過了數分鐘後，李男逐漸恢復意識。 <br />\n<br />\n警員了解後始得知，原來李男患有心臟病，之前曾做過兩次心臟手術，今年初才剛做心臟支架手術，當日他正在石家莊出差，得悉住在秦皇島的母親病重昏迷，遂趕到石家莊火車站打算回鄉。不料走到東廣場時感到心臟不適，本想服用救心丸控制病情，沒想到發病迅速打不開藥瓶。為了求助只好將鈔票撒在面前，希望引起途人注意。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180227/bkncn-20180227103900246-0227_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180227%2Fbkncn-20180227103900246-0227_05011_001.html&d=JLJRyV8gpjzNZnVJkEwOI9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1d4ff856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180227/bkncn-20180227103900246-0227_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"110e20efaff446d6b489d9cb67bda27465db32ad","tid":574192,"uid":987,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:47:50.000Z","msg":"中國最美是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec4aab4fbb6470c502a33e88db98bc2dc3bd117","tid":574192,"uid":117200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"有腦"},{"pid":"cb9777732eb0da0a1c69744e28895fddb4218b97","tid":574192,"uid":48796,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:04:52.000Z","msg":"識玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f452e81a9bea89a7299612df64426a5cc61fde42","tid":574192,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:04:58.000Z","msg":"估唔到中國都有好人"},{"pid":"ea81d7067f64093cb9b0325b17b7a6184b3d9592","tid":574192,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:06:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7e2b234eb2dc1de0f4bb5849c6f396d6621f0fa","tid":574192,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到中國都有好人</blockquote><br />\n佢有錢=幫得就幫<br />\n<br />\n無錢=選擇性失明"},{"pid":"f3a95d015082c56d8c59e148e249bdc93091bb3d","tid":574192,"uid":107181,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"好了解自己國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aea668e0c49658c23b389e1f6c3ef32a86a2838","tid":574192,"uid":26601,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"佩服，佢有資格係大陸生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3592a0c360a4f5c708042e375099ede61114ca3","tid":574192,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"唔好講笑<br />\nD路人肯定心諗依條契弟高章<br />\n知道咩叫小財唔出 大財唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09eb88fd46e265e728bc2c28c39692a88574321","tid":574192,"uid":24457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"原來心臟病會噴血架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"